Package gw.api.domain.geodata.zone

Class ZoneKey

java.lang.Object
gw.api.domain.geodata.zone.ZoneKey
public class ZoneKey extends Object
A POJO that holds the key to a zone. Due to the nature of zones, none of the other entities can directly point to zone entities. All links are soft.

Turned this into an immutable object
